_{c Assessed with the AUDIT and dichotomized into 0 = “no problem drinking”(AUDIT score of ≤15) and 1 = “problem drinking”(AUDIT score of ≥16).}
Drinking > 14 or 21 (female/male) glasses of standard units of alcohol per week and/or drinking five or more glasses of standard alcohol units per occasion at
least once per week (=binge drinking).
